snippet.title: Kriegsfront Tactics - Teaser Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now on Steam ➡️ http://bit.ly/kft-steam

Kriegsfront Tactics is a turn-based mecha strategy game set in an alternate 1970s Southeast Asia.
Build your squad, complete missions, and survive the front another day.

Developed and published by Toge Productions
